          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fairness in Forgiveness Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;revises the&nbsp;public service loan forgiveness program to expand eligibility for&nbsp;student loan forgiveness&nbsp;to include&nbsp;contractor employees who work at&nbsp;national laboratories owned by the Department of Energy. </p> <p>This bill takes effect as if enacted on October 1, 2007.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-06-04T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
